foreignText: Hic onus horret,   Ut parvis Animis & parvo Corpore majus:   Hic subit & perfert: aut virtus nomen inane est,   Aut Decus & Pretium recte petit experiens Vir.
Sic leve, sic parvum est, animum quod laudis avarum   Subruit aut reficit.
citations: Essay on Human Understanding in the Chap. on the Passions.
Foundation of Morality in Theory and Practice.
